BitCo will launch its GigUp 1Gbps Fibre Internet promotion at the MyBroadband Conference 2017. The deal will be available for one day only at the conference, on 26 October at Gallagher Estate in Midrand. BitCo Gigup is an uncapped, uncontended, and symmetrical 1Gbps fibre connection which is backed by BitCo’s 99% operational uptime guarantee. The GigUp promotion is priced at: All prices exclude VAT and a once-off installation fee of R7,800. “The launch of the 1Gbps fibre speed is a prelude to even more exciting new service offerings arriving early in 2018,” said BitCo sales director Michael Colin.